Charles Spencer Chaplin, pɛɖɛyɩ-ɩ se Charlie Chaplin kɛ [[Kewiyaɣ Kɩkpɛndaɣ (Royaume-Uni)|Krandɩ-Pretaanɩ]]-tʊ nɛ palʊla-ɩ [[Lɔndrɩ (Londres)|Lɔndrɩ]] kɛ [[ɖomaɣ fenaɣ]] 16 pɩnaɣ 1889 nɛ ɛsɩ [[saŋayɩŋ fenaɣ]] 25 pɩnaɣ 1977. Ɛyʊ ɛnɛ ɛkɛ mʊsɩ laɖu nɛ ɛlakɩ tanaʊ nɛ ɛɖʊ kɛlɛm kɛlɛmwaa yɔɔ nɛ payaɣ se [[sinimaɣ]] nɛ eluki wondʊ ɖɔɖɔ. Charlie Chaplin kɛ sinimaɣ taa sɔdʊ sɔsɔʊ nakʊyʊ pɩlɩɩna e-sinimaɣ taa weyi ɛyaa se Charlot yɔ. Charlie Chaplin paɣzɩɣ ɛ-tʊmɩyɛ labʊ yɔ pɩdɛɖɛ pɩnzɩ 65 ɛlɛ ɛwɛ kɛlɛm kɛlɛmnaa sakɩyɛ taa nɛ pɛɖɛ ɛzɩ 80 yɔ nɛ ɛ-ɖonɛ nɛ e-wezu caɣʊ nɛ taa yeba nɛ nabayɩ tɔŋ se ɛkɩlaɣ ɖɛlɛzɩɣ ɖɔm. 

